      "content": "Your point highlights the existential crisis that can arise from confronting the impermanence of human existence. Some people may continue to seek meaning and connection as a form of self-delusion or coping mechanism, rather than an authentic attempt to grasp the nature of reality. It's a bleak sentiment, but it's one that many have grappled with throughout history. The darkness can be overwhelming.",
      "source": "target",
